==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: The same kind of rice provides for one hundred kinds of people.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī yàng mĭ yăng băi yàng rén

===Phrase===
'''[[一样]][[米]][[养]][[百]][[样]][[人]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Everybody thinks a little differently.

===Alternate forms===
[[一樣]][[米]][[養]][[百]][[樣]][[人]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

